{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData.append()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/append","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><em><code>append()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<code><strong>append()</strong></code>&nbsp; da&nbsp;Interface&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a> &nbsp;adiciona um novo valor&nbsp;dentro de uma chave existente dentro do objeto&nbsp;<code>FormData&nbsp;</code>ou &nbsp;adiciona a &nbsp;chave caso ainda não exista.</p>\n\n<p>A diferença entre &nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>FormData.set</code></a> e <code>append()</code> é que se uma&nbsp; chave específica já exista, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>FormData.set</code></a> irá&nbsp;substituir o valor existente com um novo valor, já o&nbsp;<code>append()</code> irá&nbsp;adicionar&nbsp;um novo valor&nbsp;no fim do&nbsp;conjunto de valores.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Nota</strong>: Este &nbsp;metodo esta desponivel&nbsp;no&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Existe duas versoes deste metodo: um de dois e um outro de tres:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> filename<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"append_parameters","title":"Parametros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd>O nome do campo cujos dados estão contidas em value.</dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code></dt>\n <dd>O valor deste campo . Nas duas versões este é a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>USVString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, ou &nbsp;caso não seja , este é convertido em string. Na versão&nbsp;de tres parametros este pode ser&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>, ou &nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>USVString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, de novo, caso nenhum deses&nbsp;forem especificados &nbsp;este valor é convertido em uma&nbsp;string.</dd>\n <dt id=\"filename\"><code>filename </code><span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>O filename&nbsp;reporta para o servidor (a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>USVString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>), quando&nbsp;a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> ou&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> é&nbsp;passado como o segundo parametro. O default&nbsp;filename para &nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> o objecto é \"blob\".</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Nota:</strong> Se espisificares &nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> como a data append &nbsp;para o objecto&nbsp;<code>FormData</code>&nbsp;, o filename a ser reportado para o servidor &nbsp;no \"Content-Disposition\" header usado para mudar de browser em browser.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"retorna","title":"Retorna","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Void.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>As seguintes&nbsp;linhas criam um Objecto&nbsp;<code>FormData</code> vazio:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FormData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Corrente vazio</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Podes adicionar chaves/valores pares para usar (domxref(\"FormData.append\")}}:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Chris'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'userpic'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myFileInput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'chris.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estato</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentario</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-formdata-append\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'append()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Caracteristicas</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Basico</td>\n   <td>7+</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>10+</td>\n   <td>12+</td>\n   <td>5+</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>append com filename</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/22\" title=\"Released on 2013-06-25.\">22.0</a> (22.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Disponivel para Desenvolvedores Web</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" title=\"Released on 2015-06-30.\">39.0</a> (39.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Caracteristicas</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome para Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>3.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td>1.0.1</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>12+</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>append com filename</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/22\" title=\"Released on 2013-06-25.\">22.0</a> (22.0)</td>\n   <td>1.2</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">Disponivel para Desenvolvedores Web</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" title=\"Released on 2015-06-30.\">39.0</a> (39.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect6\">\n<p><strong>Nota</strong>: XHR em &nbsp;Android 4.0 envia conteudo vazio &nbsp;para FormData com blob.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_gecko","title":"Notas Gecko","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Antis do Gecko&nbsp;7.0 (Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4), se especificares <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>&nbsp;como a conteudo a ser &nbsp;adicionado ao objecto, o filename reportado no \"Content-Disposition\"&nbsp;HTTP header era um string vazio; este resulta em &nbsp;erros sendo reportados por alguns servidores. Começando com&nbsp;Gecko 7.0, o filename \"blob\" é enviado.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_tambem","title":"Veja Tambem","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\" title=\"Using XMLHttpRequest\">Usando XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\" title=\"DOM/XMLHttpRequest/FormData/Using_FormData_objects\">UsandoFormData objects</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja Tambem","id":"veja_tambem"}],"summary":"O método append()  da Interface FormData  adiciona um novo valor dentro de uma chave existente dentro do objeto FormData ou  adiciona a  chave caso ainda não exista.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FormData.append()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/formdata/append","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/formdata/append/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData","title":"FormData"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData/append","title":"FormData.append()"}],"pageTitle":"FormData.append() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}